---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import { snapshots, formatSnapshotDate } from '../lib/portfolio';
---
<Layout title="Dashboard" description="Progressively enhanced legacy dashboard shell with native context and next-step guidance.">
<section class="command-hero rounded-[2rem] border border-primary/20 bg-base-200 p-6 md:p-10 shadow-2xl mb-8"><p class="badge badge-primary badge-lg mb-4">Legacy + native shell</p><h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-black mb-4">The original dashboard, framed with production context.</h1><p class="max-w-3xl text-lg text-base-content/75">The embedded panel preserves the legacy Jekyll dashboard and client-side GitHub API behavior. Native Astro routes now provide static-first stats, discussions, docs, and board views around it.</p></section>
<section class="grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-3 mb-8"><div class="card bg-base-200 shadow-xl"><div class="card-body"><h2 class="card-title">Native snapshot layer</h2><p>Stats, discussions, and board pages read committed JSON for fast first paint.</p><p class="text-xs text-base-content/60">Stats: {formatSnapshotDate(snapshots.stats.fetchedAt)}</p></div></div><div class="card bg-base-200 shadow-xl"><div class="card-body"><h2 class="card-title">Legacy frame</h2><p>Preserved original UI with browser cache and live GitHub calls where available.</p></div></div><div class="card bg-base-200 shadow-xl"><div class="card-body"><h2 class="card-title">Go next</h2><div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2"><a class="btn btn-sm btn-primary" href="/statistics">Stats</a><a class="btn btn-sm btn-outline" href="/development-board">Board</a><a class="btn btn-sm btn-outline" href="/docs">Docs</a></div></div></div></section>
<div class="rounded-[2rem] border border-base-content/10 bg-base-200 p-3 shadow-2xl"><div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-3 p-3"><div><h2 class="font-bold">Legacy dashboard viewport</h2><p class="text-sm text-base-content/60">Scrollable embedded app; open directly if you need full-screen legacy behavior.</p></div><a class="btn btn-sm btn-outline" href="/legacy/index.html">Open legacy</a></div><iframe src="/legacy/index.html" title="Legacy portfolio dashboard" class="w-full rounded-2xl border border-base-content/10 bg-base-100" style="min-height:min(760px,80vh)"></iframe></div>
</Layout>
